{"tid":2332229,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"「一生只能活一次！」美國太空軍軍官為搶購 PS5 而被降級","createTime":"2020-12-19T12:35:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T15:40:18.000Z","uid":105678,"like":22,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"cfef4a9476a4f51943b5685c7d26e1869b8454b8","tid":2332229,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T12:35:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vpot8er.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVpot8er.jpg&h=a71b0ab5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPlayStation 5 一機難求，機價被炒高一倍。每有訂購活動，名額都會被秒殺一空。據一個專門報道美軍消息的 Facebook 專頁報道，美國太空軍一名前高級飛行員日前為了四出搶購 PS5 ，在體能訓練課程中遲到 35 分鐘，因而受訓斥並且軍階被降一級。<br />\n<br />\n據專頁貼出的警戒信指出，這名前高級飛行員平時已經經常遲到，態度不佳。而在事發當日，他不單遲到，還向上司發出一段「自尋死路」的回應：「一生只能活一次， PS5&gt;警戒信」，最終他果然收到了一封警戒信，而且軍階更由 E-4 高級飛行員，降級至 E-3 一級飛行員，薪金少了約 $220 美元，大約夠他每個月買半部正價 PS5 。<br />\n<br />\n美國軍方發言人沒有證實這宗事件，但就表示網上那封警戒信符合美軍文件格式。"},{"pid":"e75af4323dad079b9827fa117c29343c8e262728","tid":2332229,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T12:36:49.000Z","msg":"正確態度"},{"pid":"b77fe7e3824f48e36e0b69b8f96c13d4553e8d1a","tid":2332229,"uid":200529,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T12:38:10.000Z","msg":"respect"},{"pid":"a97aa1b567f3036644b0848896e3e4584a2683e8","tid":2332229,"uid":71085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T12:38:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dcbe2a8344f86ce4a50b84fdcfc5eaf4ffa09397","tid":2332229,"uid":66365,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T12:39:22.000Z","msg":"買完都無驚玩架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42dea9af665716f950d3592cd7117e32187e8e8b","tid":2332229,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T12:39:31.000Z","msg":"一生只能活一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美國態度"},{"pid":"cf63e1a9ed9b7636398ef5ed00826d39d0fef51d","tid":2332229,"uid":1700